OL,6,FBurial records obtained by an ITV News
OL,7,FFreedom of Information Request showed
OL,8,F45 babies who were born and died at
OL,9,Fthe home are buried in a mass unmarked
OL,10,Fgrave.
OL,12,FWe also heard allegations from three
OL,13,Fdifferent sources - including a family
OL,14,Fmember - that mothers were denied
OL,15,Fmodern medical care and babies with
OL,16,Fdisabilities were left to die in agony.
OL,18,FTim Farron, the MP for Westmorland and
OL,19,FLonsdale, wants Cumbria Police to
OL,20,Finvestigate what happened at the home
OL,21,Fover its 52 year history
